re. Ett kj\u00f8ret\u00f8y ble avskiltet grunnet manglende periodisk kontroll.", "F\u00f8lg Adresseavisen p\u00e5 Facebook , Instagram og Twitter ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b75fd3af27519413eb0e7b6175f6ab60a7df266a57e5c68ece18eecb1555081a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-20T20:56:55.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Statens vegvesen er ikke imponert etter \u00e5 ha hatt kontroll p\u00e5 E6 i \u00c5sen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12565444.ece/bkt27a/ALTERNATES/w980-default/overlast.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b7853f50b8f48d80131e88514ce5fdd17c569401.jpg?58d04217"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det f\u00f8rer til mer slitasje p\u00e5 veiene -adressa.no", "- \u00d8konomisk fordel", "Kj\u00f8rte uten bombrikke"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b7853f50b8f48d80131e88514ce5fdd17c569401"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Statens vegvesen", "E6", "\u00c5sen", "Tungtransport"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Statens vegvesen,E6,\u00c5sen,Tungtransport"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["\u00f8konomisk fordel", "kontroll", "kj\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["tungtransport", "statens", "\u00e5sen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["nord-tr\u00f8ndelag", "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "roar susegg"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12565444.ece/bkt27a/ALTERNATES/w980-default/overlast.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "